Package: xfce4-claude-status-plugin
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: XFCE panel plugin showing Claude Max/Pro usage limits
 Displays Claude API rate limit usage (5-hour and 7-day windows)
 with colored progress bars in the XFCE panel.
 .
 Requires Claude Code to be installed and logged in with a
 Max or Pro subscription.
